(33, '5 basic Emotional Intelligence competencies PMP® need to success at work in the 60 PDUs online course', '5-basic-emotional-intelligence-competencies-pmp-need-to-success-at-work-in-the-60-pdus-online-course', '60-PDUs-online-course.jpg', 'Do you think you’re qualified for your project management job? Do you know the concept of Emotional Intelligent (EI)? Do you apply EI in your project management work? Do you know the importance of Emotional Intelligence (EI) to a Project Management Professional (PMP®)?', '<h2><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Do you think you’re qualified for your project management job? Do you know the concept of Emotional Intelligent (EI)? Do you apply EI in your project management work? Do you know the importance of Emotional Intelligence (EI) to a Project Management Professional (PMP</span><span style="font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">®</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">)?</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 13px;"><img alt="5 basic Emotional Intelligence competencies PMP® need to success at work in the 60 PDUs online course" src="/public/images/articles/60-PDUs-online-course.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Emotional Intelligence (EI) is, in short, awareness of one’s own emotions and moods and those of others, especially in managing people. Emotional intelligence is the critical distinction between great leaders and people that have risen in the hierarchy based on their position (Daniel Goleman. What Makes a Leader. Harvard Business Review, 2004)</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Stevbros Training and Consultancy – PMP</span><span style="font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">®</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"> Registered Education Provider (PMI R.E.P # 3807) introduce Emotional Intelligence (EI) for Project Management Professional (PMP</span><span style="font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">®</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">) and explain how Emotional Intelligence (EI) helps Project Management Professional (PMP</span><span style="font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">®</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">) advance in their professional career in the online training course:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/60-pdus-renew-pmp-certificate-after-every-3-years-lowest-price.html">60 PDUs for PMP® Certificate Renewal</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/60-pdus-renew-pmp-certificate-after-every-3-years-lowest-price.html"><img alt="5 basic Emotional Intelligence competencies PMP® need to success at work in the 60 PDUs online course" src="/public/images/articles/easiest-way-to-earn-pdu-pmp-pmi.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 284px;" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/60-pdus-renew-pmp-certificate-after-every-3-years-lowest-price.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 141, 183); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">60 PDUs for&nbsp;PMP® Certificate Renewal. Course ID: iRPC. Price: $60</em></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Here are brief introduction of 5 basic Emotional Intelligence (EI) competencies PMP</span><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16px;">® need to success at work:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color:#008080;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Self-awareness</span></span>: is the ability to recognize and monitor our thoughts and feelings. You recognize your moods and emotions, and conduct a realistic self-assessment</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:#008080;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Self-regulation</span></span>: is the ability to think before acting, handle change and uncertainty. It entails suspending snap judgments and impulsive decisions and choices.</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:#008080;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Motivation</span></span>: is the ability to guide people towards the goals, help people continuously improve and conquer all obstacles.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color:#008080;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Empathy</span></span>: is the ability to sense what people feel, understand their perspective, and cultivate rapport with a broad diversity of people.</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:#008080;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Social skills</span></span>: is ability to manage groups of people, find common ground with various stakeholders, and build rapport.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Read more:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/6-reasons-you-should-earn-60-pdus-for-pmp-recertification.html">6 reasons you should earn 60 PDUs for PMP® recertification</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/3-most-important-things-pmps-need-from-pmp-pdu-online-course.html">3 most important things PMP® need from PMP® PDU online course</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em style="text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Access&nbsp;<a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 141, 183); text-decoration: none;">blog of project management training&nbsp;here!</a></em></p>\r\n', '2013-11-17 07:06:12', '2013-11-17 07:17:26', 1, '5 basic Emotional Intelligence competencies PMP® need to success at work in the 60 PDUs online course', 0, NULL, ',15,18,', 'phuong', 'phuong', 0),
