(36, '5 reasons why people fail in PMP® certification exam', '5-top-reasons-why-people-fail-in-pmp-certification-exam', 'reasons-why-people-fail-PMP-certification-exam.jpg', 'Most of people want to know the reasons before choosing a training course to earn 35 pre-approved contact hours for application document of PMP® certification exam while some of people want to know the reasons before taking PMP® certification exam.', '<h2><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Stevbros has received this question many times: why people fail in PMP</span>®<span style="line-height: 1.6em;"> certification exam. Most of them want to know the reasons before choosing a training course to<a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html"> earn 35 pre-approved contact hours for application document of PMP</a></span><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html">® certification</a><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html"> exam</a> while some of them want to know the reasons before taking PMP</span>®<span style="line-height: 1.6em;"> certification exam.</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="5 top reasons why people fail in PMP® certification exam" src="/public/images/articles/reasons-why-people-fail-PMP-certification-exam.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 282px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are 5 reasons why people fail in <strong>PMP® certification exam</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><em style="line-height: 1.6em;">1)</em><em style="line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</em></span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Read wrong book</span>: before taking the exam, you must attain<a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html"> </a></span><em style="line-height: 1.6em;"><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html">35 education hours (35 education hours provided by PMI R.E.P in the course of 35 Professional Development Units (PDUs) are called 35 pre-approved contact hours)</a>.</em><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"> The content of the course you choose must align to the last edition of PMBOK. You can choose to read 1 or 2 more books if you want. However, the lasted edition of PMBOK is the must and you should read no more than 3 books related to PMP</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">®</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"> Exam Prep.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;">2)&nbsp;&nbsp; Answer the question with your experience</span>: you of-course must be an experienced project managers to become eligible for PMP® certification exam. However, are you sure that your experience are right 100%?&nbsp;You may did something wrong in your professional career. So, to pass PMP® certification exam, you should read <a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/the-competencies-of-project-managers-according-to-the-pmbok-guide.html">the lasted edition of PMBOK carefully</a>, identify the gaps in your knowledge, fulfill the gaps that may hurt you in the PMP® certification exam, and answer the questions confidently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;">3)&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not remember processes and/or do not understand purpose of processes in PMBOK</span>: Now PMBOK is in the fifth edition, it comprises of 47 processes, which are categorized into 5 process groups and 10 knowledge areas. <a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/3-most-important-things-of-pmp-35-pre-approved-contact-hours-online-course.html">Learning by heart and understand purpose of 47 processes </a>help increase the chance of your success in PMP® certification exam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;">4)&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not understand concepts, terms, rules of thumbs and formulas in PMBOK</span>: a <a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/3-most-important-things-of-pmp-35-pre-approved-contact-hours-online-course.html">checklist of those things</a> will help you a lot in the PMP® certification exam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;">5)&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not manage time well</span>: A&nbsp;typical common mistake during PMP<span style="font-size: 13px;">® certification exam</span> is spending too much time to read the question. Remember you only have 4 hours for 200 questions. You earn the same score for every correct answer. Be smart to allocate your adequate time into each question. 1 minute for 1 question is recommend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.stevbros.com/payment/pmp-exam-prep-35-pdus-lowest-price.html"><img alt="5 top reasons why people fail in PMP® certification exam" src="/public/images/articles/PMP-Exam-Prep-Online-35-PDU-lowest-price.jpg" style="width: 599px; height: 345px;" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">PMP® exam preparation 35 PDUs. Price $35.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stevbros deeply understands reasons people fail in PMP® certificate exam and designs an online course to help you earn <a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/5-reasons-you-should-study-pmp-35-pre-approved-contact-hours-online.html">35 pre-approved contact hours</a> and prepare PMP® certification exam effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="view_post" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 22px; list-style: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Access&nbsp;<a href="http://www.stevbros.com/project-management-training/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 141, 183); text-decoration: none;">blog of project management training&nbsp;here</a>