(52, 'PMBOK® 5th Edition Refresh', 'pmbok-5th-edition-refresh', 'pmp-exam-prep-pmbok5.jpg', 'Duration: 5-day workshop + 25-hour e-learning. Who should attend: this course is designed for PMP® who took the PMP® Exam in PMBOK® 4th edition or older, and PMBOK® practitioner using PMBOK® 4th edition or older.', '<p><span style="color:#B22222;"><strong>Duration: 5-day workshop + 25-hour e-learning, earn 60 PDUs.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Who should attend: this course is designed for&nbsp;PMP<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">® who took the&nbsp;</span>PMP<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">® Exam in&nbsp;</span>PMBOK<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">® 4th edition or older one, and&nbsp;</span>PMBOK<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: small; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">® </span>practitioner using&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 13px;">PMBOK</span><span style="font-size: small; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">® 4th edition or older one.</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="PMBOK Project Management Fundamentals" src="http://www.stevbros.com/public/images/articles/stevbros-project-management-in-house-training.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; width: 600px; height: 279px;" title="Effective project management skills" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; li